eejar
=====

Utility to create a Maven-based project skeleton for a Jar with additional configuration,
logging and other support automatically configured.

Prerequisites
-------------

An installed copy of Ruby to generate the project skeleton.

An installed copy of Maven 2.x to run and test the project

To run
------

For a Jar-based project:

./eejar

For a simple servlet-based (WAR) project:

./eewar

For a SpringMVC-based (WAR) project:

./eespringwar

